        <statement>
          <p>
            Jack has made <m>23</m> dozen Christmas cookies so far and is making more at a steady rate of <m>5</m> dozen per hour.
            Jill has made <m>11</m> dozen and is making more at a rate of <m>9</m> dozen per hour.
            Assuming they both continue at this same pace,
            when will they both have the same number of cookies?
          </p>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>
            <m>3</m> hours from now
          </p>
